          <div>
            <a href="/tax/sales-tax-calculator">Sales Tax Calculator</a>
            <p>Calculate US sales tax on any purchase or reverse the total back to the pre-tax price, with a full table of state rates.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
